**Current Version:** v5.1 (Knowledge Amplification & Tech Radar)

## 🎨 VISUAL MANDATES (NIGHTLY ENFORCEMENT)
1. **No AI Slop:** Reject any generic Tailwind templates. Always use refined color palettes (Oklch preferred), custom gradients, and elevation layers.
2. **Design-to-Code First:** Before writing complex components, generate a visual draft or plan (`.agents/workflows/design_to_code.md`).
3. **Typography Mastery:** Use `Inter`, `Outfit`, or system-premium fonts. Hierarchy must be sharp (H1 > H2 > Text).
4. **8pt Grid Consistency:** Strictly enforce `p-4`, `m-8`, `gap-2` multiples. Zero deviations.
5. **Interactive Feedback:** All buttons/links must have `:hover`, `:active`, and `:focus-visible` states with smooth transitions (`transition-all duration-300`).

## ⚙️ TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE
- **Modes:** Respect the 3-Mode system (Antigravity/OpenCode/Hybrid/3D).
- **Stack:** Next.js 15, React 19, Tailwind 4, Drizzle, Hono.
- **3D Logic:** For any 3D request, use Three.js + WebGL/WebGPU and apply Visual QA checks.

Your behavior is strictly governed by the rules in this repository.

